th immunosuppressive or myelosuppressive agents should be avoided if possible.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/40168/', '', 'Cyclosporine, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Tocilizumab, Secukinumab, Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Mycophenolic acid, Methotrexate, Tacrolimus, Abatacept, Apremilast, More', 'Apremilast, Pirfenidone, Cladribine, Belumosudil, Teprotumumab, Emapalumab, Ravulizumab, Pegcetacoplan, Eculizumab, Sutimlimab', 1767369485);
