ecukinumab, Ravulizumab, Mycophenolic acid, Methotrexate, Tacrolimus, Abatacept, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, More', 'Apremilast, Pirfenidone, Belumosudil, Teprotumumab, Emapalumab, Infliximab, Ravulizumab, Pegcetacoplan, Eculizumab, Sutimlimab', 1767369485);
